{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "corporate_communication", "channel": "pr_and_media_relations", "user": "andrew.park", "message": "We need to schedule a press release for our new store opening in Toronto next month. Any ideas on the best date and time?", "created_at": 1620500000001}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "corporate_communication", "channel": "pr_and_media_relations", "user": "john_smith", "message": "How about we do it on the 15th at 10 am? That's usually when we get the highest engagement on our social media platforms.", "created_at": 1620500000002}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sustainability_initiatives", "channel": "waste_management", "user": "jane_doe", "message": "I've finished the initial assessment for our waste management at the Vancouver branch. We are currently recycling 60% of our waste, which is a 5% improvement from last quarter.", "created_at": 1620500000003}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "corporate_communication", "channel": "pr_and_media_relations", "user": "andrew.park", "message": "Great suggestion, John. Let's go with the 15th at 10 am. I'll start drafting the press release.", "created_at": 1620500000004}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sustainability_initiatives", "channel": "waste_management", "user": "andrew.park", "message": "Good progress on the waste management, Jane. Can we aim for a 10% increase by end of the year?", "created_at": 1620500000005}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "corporate_communication", "channel": "pr_and_media_relations", "user": "john_smith", "message": "I'll coordinate with the social media team to make sure we're maximizing our reach for the press release.", "created_at": 1620500000006}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sustainability_initiatives", "channel": "waste_management", "user": "jane_doe", "message": "10% sounds like a good target, Andrew. I'll revise our waste management plan accordingly.", "created_at": 1620500000007}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sustainability_initiatives", "channel": "waste_management", "user": "jane_doe", "message": "Good morning team, I've just received the final report from our third-party environmental review. It seems we have a significant challenge ahead of us. Our stores collectively generated over 4200 tons of packaging waste last year. Shockingly, more than 80% of this is not made from recycled materials.", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sustainability_initiatives", "channel": "waste_management", "user": "andrew.park", "message": "Thanks for sharing this, Jane. It's indeed a significant concern. As we move towards positioning Lee's Market as an ethical alternative to larger retailers, we need to address this issue head-on. We'll need a robust strategy to reduce our waste and increase our use of recycled materials. Let's discuss this further in our next meeting.", "create_at": 1620501000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "corporate_communication", "channel": "pr_and_media_relations", "user": "andrew.park", "message": "Team, we need to be mindful about how we communicate our sustainability efforts. The recent report on our waste generation could pose a reputational risk if not handled strategically. We need to be transparent about our current situation, but also emphasize our commitment to improving. Let's align our messages with our actions and use this as an opportunity to position Lee's Market as a responsible retailer.", "create_at": 1620502000000}}
